        <updateDate>2019-11-18T20:30:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Funding Local Assistance and Recovery Efforts Act or the</b> <b>FLARE Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Agriculture to make retroactive payments to states and local governments under the emergency watershed protection program for work that is done after a project is approved, but before funds are dispersed.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
